            { type = "p", text = "Housing Decor" },
            { type = "p", text = "10 Illusionary Coins" },
            { type = "hr" },
            { type = "p", text = "You might not defeat the Void and save Azeroth by taking part in this event, but it’s a great way to find a bit of fun in the face of the ever-present threat the Void presents. We’ll see you…or maybe not… in Decor Duels." },
